## 8. Business Requirements

### BR-01 Worker Management

The system must allow ops teams to **create, update, activate, and deactivate workers** without document dependency.

---

### BR-02 Job Management

The system must allow ops teams to **define work units**, assign workers, and **explicitly close jobs**.

---

### BR-03 Income Guarantee

The system must enforce **minimum income guarantees** and transparently calculate top-ups when earnings fall below thresholds.

---

### BR-04 Payment Execution

The system must enable **same-day or scheduled payments**, track transaction status, and surface failures.

---

### BR-05 Work History & Audit

The system must maintain an **immutable, append-only ledger** of work and payments.

---

### BR-06 Reporting

The system must provide **exportable reports** for operational review and compliance.

---

## 9. Business Rules

| Rule               | Description                                  |
| ------------------ | -------------------------------------------- |
| Explicit actions   | No silent automation                         |
| Immutability       | Payments and ledger entries cannot be edited |
| Forward-only rules | Income rules apply only to future work       |
| Accountability     | All actions logged                           |
| Manual override    | Allowed but auditable                        |

---

## 10. Assumptions

* Institutions fund income guarantees
* Ops teams are trained power users
* Desktop usage is acceptable
